---
title: Moroccan-Style Chickpea & Tomato Stew with Lemony Yogurt & Garlic Pitas
description: We can’t get enough of the aromatic, richly-spiced flavors of Moroccan cuisine—so we’re channeling them into a steamy, hearty stew that’s sure to warm you from the inside out. Carrot, onion, and chickpeas are seasoned with garlic powder, earthy cumin, spicy chili flakes, fresh ginger, umami-packed tomato paste, and a smoky cinnamon paprika spice blend, then simmered in a tomato broth until thickened. It’s all dolloped with lemony yogurt and served with garlicky toasted pitas for dipping, because you won’t want to let a drop of this stew go to waste.
